On a kind and serious note Body shaming is no joke people are struggling with so many problems hence why they gain weight on some are very skinny infact it’s a very huge sin aswell body shaming and skin shaming somebody. 

Last Eid I met my phupo who made me very conscious about my weight that I almost stopped eating and I got very sick aswell and lost good weight and last night as somebody complimented me that I look fit she yelled and disagreed to it that made me realise people do this just to make us uncomfortable so. Live and let live. 

One of my very old friend years back took her own life because she couldn’t take people’s shaming on her body because she was battling with a few medical conditions that made her very healthy.
